[node name="notes 0 lane" type="Node" parent="." node_paths=PackedStringArray("default_button")]
script = ExtResource("3_yjt82")
rich_text = "This is a [as]lane[/as].

[as]notes[/as] fall from the top of the lane to the bottom.
[as]notes[/as] can also be diffrent speeds."
character_name = "Asahi"
default_button = NodePath("../defbtn")
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://dtkvtfngw82l5"

[node name="notes 1 key" type="Node" parent="." node_paths=PackedStringArray("default_button")]
script = ExtResource("3_yjt82")
rich_text = "This is a [as]key[/as].

As soon as the [as]note[/as] touches the [as]key[/as], you need to press the [as]lane[/as]'s corresponding button.

The keys are:
- lane 1: [as]D[/as] (leftmost lane)
- lane 2: [as]F[/as] (middle-left lane)
- lane 3: [as]J[/as] (middle-right lane)
- lane 4:: [as]K[/as] (rightmost lane)"
character_name = "Asahi"
default_button = NodePath("../defbtn")
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://dtkvtfngw82l5"

[node name="notes 2 judge" type="Node" parent="." node_paths=PackedStringArray("default_button")]
script = ExtResource("3_yjt82")
rich_text = "If you do it correctly, the [as]note[/as] will disappear and you will be awarded a [as]hit[/as].
If you're too late, the [as]note[/as] will disappear and you will be awarded a [as]miss[/as]."
character_name = "Asahi"
default_button = NodePath("../defbtn")
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://dtkvtfngw82l5"

[node name="notes 3 combo" type="Node" parent="." node_paths=PackedStringArray("default_button")]
script = ExtResource("3_yjt82")
rich_text = "This is your [as]combo[/as].

This number goes up by [i]one[/i] when you [as]hit[/as]
(why does that sound wrong...)

It resets back to [i]zero[/i] when you [as]miss[/as]."
character_name = "Asahi"
default_button = NodePath("../defbtn")
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://dtkvtfngw82l5"

[node name="notes 4 score" type="Node" parent="." node_paths=PackedStringArray("default_button")]
script = ExtResource("3_yjt82")
rich_text = "This is your [as]score[/as].

It goes up or down by a certain amount when you [as]hit[/as] or [as]miss[/as] notes."
character_name = "Asahi"
default_button = NodePath("../defbtn")
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://dtkvtfngw82l5"

